original_title: Nine Indian fishermen arrested in Jaffna
original_body_lines: COLOMBO (News 1st); Nine Indian fishermen have been arrested for illegally fishing near Delft Island, Jaffna.
The fishermen and vessels will be handed over to the Fisheries Department.
Court prevents protest in Fort; Trade Unions continue protest despite rainfall
Newsline | Non Essential Imports must be curbed | Prof. Lalithasiri Gunaruwan | 24th July 2023
